  - Requires attribution to Voix in product documentation
  - Covers SaaS, embedded, and OEM distributions
  - Contact: daedaevibin@naver.com

## License Selection
By default, all use is under AGPLv3. For commercial licensing:
1. Contact Dae Euhwa at daedaevibin@naver.com
2. Provide product details and expected revenue
3. Execute commercial license agreement

